的大律師石書銘盤問下表示，他在醫院時有相機隨身，但拍完警長傷勢照片後，「相機運作唔到」，無法拍攝證物，遂打算返回辦公室容後處理。其後「工作真係太繁忙，新舊案都要同時處理，唔記得咗幫啲證物影相」。<br />\n<br />\n他承認在處理證物上有疏忽，並同意玻璃樽及裝有易燃液體的膠樽沒有放入防干擾證物袋中，亦沒有另一證物警員在場作證。石大狀稱：「所有處理證物嘅規則，你都違反晒；除咗你，冇人可以講得出啲液體喺邊度嚟。」蘇同意辯方說法。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200921/AHARAXCEO5HQZNMCVRHIJT2JOE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200921%2FAHARAXCEO5HQZNMCVRHIJT2JOE%2F&d=UI3sabJMorhQDzR%2BXF3zEQp4YzggAwntK9UjHSQ2u7w%3D&h=e749d6d6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200921%2FAHARAXCEO5HQZNMCVRHIJT2JOE%2F&h=c3062a13\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200921/AHARAXCEO5HQZNMCVRHIJT2JOE/</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T15:44:03.000Z","msg":"黒警：平時砌生豬肉都係自己買野返嚟整架啦，邊有咁煩。"},{"pid":"cfab5a37ec7fb28a59db229b18e02fe0c07dfb08","tid":2212120,"uid":61032,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T15:49:53.000Z","msg":"處理證物程序咁複雜，毅進仔既智商邊度handle到<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"edebc6c40ce86b80e935b34031bfcc43f9c25803","tid":2212120,"uid":25825,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T15:54:49.000Z","msg":"a"},{"pid":"270e8dff0f1c979bda94b7bb099af39e0e6ec9bc","tid":2212120,"uid":25825,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T15:55:18.000Z","msg":"A"},{"pid":"e0d5e79d89b48c6f82ad27b4cd45f983d9569ee4","tid":2212120,"uid":25825,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T15:55:35.000Z","msg":"S"},{"pid":"cda7dcd55fe7861bf38503b47dac2a3271b1db52","tid":2212120,"uid":25825,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T15:56:00.000Z","msg":"A"},{"pid":"e74eab7d293f5b09fe97168d0ebcd76202eaec64","tid":2212120,"uid":25825,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T15:56:14.000Z","msg":"A"},{"p